translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なにを言っているんだ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What are you talking about?
...Apparently, from how it feels,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まったく時間が経っていないようだすね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: no time has passed at all.
Haah, good grief.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなことで遊ばず、テラを探すか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Instead of playing around like this, shall we look for Terra?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まだそんなこと言っているのか……ﾇﾇﾇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're still saying that...? Nn-nn-nn.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「当たり前だ！　お前らの女王を探すんだろうが！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course! You're looking for your queen, aren't you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いい加減この船を荒らすようなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you keep wrecking this ship,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こっちにだって考えがあるぞ！　ﾇﾇﾇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've got my own ideas too! Nn-nn-nn!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えーい、やかましい。次はこれだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh, be quiet. Next is this.
There, click!
Geez, you two, enough already...—
Hah!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 轟音と共にメガワスの体が吹き飛ばされた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a roar, Megawas’s body was blown away.
What!?
I-it’s a device!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 装置の中に誰かがいます！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone's inside the device!
—Nuht, suddenly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 装置から異形の化け物が姿を現す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A grotesque monster appeared from the device.
J-Jaharukkas... Nn-nn-nn.
What!? Is this it!?
Death-death-death-death - shishishi...
Kill, still kill, kill a lot...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 殺す？　否、殺さなければ、殺す……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kill? No, if I don't kill, I will kill...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まだ足りぬ、足りない、死死死死……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Not enough yet, insufficient, death death death death...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだぁ、わけの分からんことばかり……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What the heck, it's all nonsense...
The moment it spoke,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異形の巨大な双眼がランス達に向けられる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The grotesque giant twin eyes locked onto Rance and the others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひっ！　ランス様、こっち見てますよ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eek! Lord Rance, it's looking at us!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちっ、やるしかなさそうだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tch, looks like we have no choice but to fight.
Shaaaaaaaaah!!
Tch...
This is really frustrating!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな雑魚に手間取るな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don’t waste time on such weaklings!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本当の戦いというものを見せてやる！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll show you what a real battle is!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「サテラさん！　助けてくれるんですか！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Satera! Are you going to help us!?
Hmph, don’t get the wrong idea.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 焦れったいから今回は手を貸すだけだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’m just helping this time because it’s annoying.
Now, let’s go, Caesar!
Crush everything!
Yes, Lady Satera.
U-um, Lord Rance...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっと待って下さい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please wait a moment.
Jaharukkas's condition is...
Hmph, I can tell just by looking.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいつ、生意気にも大技を繰り出す気だな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That guy arrogantly intends to use a big technique.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （かなみの手裏剣でぴよらせるか、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Should I stun it with Kanami’s shuriken,
defeat it before it uses the big attack,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、確実に防御してしのぐか……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: or no, block reliably and endure...)
(Hmmm...)
Gwooooooooh!!!!
Why!?
Why is it me against idiots like these...!
N-no way... could it be true...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あのジャハルッカスを倒せるのか？　ﾇﾇﾇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can they really defeat that Jaharukkas? Nn-nn-nn.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やっぱりただ者じゃないわ、この人達……ﾇﾇﾇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As I thought, these people are no ordinary folks... Nn-nn-nn.
